No. D-2619. In the Matter of Discipline of David E. Fox. 565 U.S. 1107, 132 S. Ct. 1086,

181 L. Ed. 2d 804,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 433. January 9, 2012.

David E. Fox, of Washington, District of Columbia, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
